}],"content":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">Hi&nbsp;{{contact.first_name}},</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);text-align: start;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;\" data-start=\"650\" data-end=\"760\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">I've got a new deal I'm sharing with a small group before it goes wide.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);text-align: start;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;\" data-start=\"650\" data-end=\"760\"></p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);text-align: start;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;\" data-start=\"650\" data-end=\"760\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">641 Powder Springs St in Smyrna, GA - 14 unit apartment building.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);text-align: start;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;\" data-start=\"650\" data-end=\"760\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">The Play: Buy below market, renovate, raise rents, improve operations.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);text-align: start;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;\" data-start=\"650\" data-end=\"760\"></p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);text-align: start;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;\" data-start=\"650\" data-end=\"760\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">LP investors get:</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);text-align: start;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;\" data-start=\"650\" data-end=\"760\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">📉 <strong data-start=\"266\" data-end=\"287\">6% Preferred Return&nbsp;</strong>(You get paid first)</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);text-align: start;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;\" data-start=\"650\" data-end=\"760\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">🏘️ <strong data-start=\"391\" data-end=\"416\">70/30 Split After That</strong> (70% LP, 30% GP)</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);text-align: start;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: auto;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust: a